Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.85,0:00:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到還能同你對戰 這也是命運吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.21,0:00:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時欠下的債 必須要還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的傀儡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.84,0:00:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 那具軀體也毫無意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.77,0:00:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我已經是不死之身 如同真正的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.79,0:00:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我渴求已久的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.22,0:00:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.09,0:00:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 那個根的人腹中也有那些粘土
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.40,0:00:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說雷遁能克制迪達拉的起爆粘土
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.99,0:00:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我或許能起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.24,0:01:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一段 用巖守護好傷者和桐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐專心治療 知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.80,0:01:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚了 喝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.55,0:01:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.51,0:01:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑秘技.山椒魚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.74,0:01:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先增援…擊潰敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐治 外面怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.32,0:03:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題 能感覺到查克拉 大家都活著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.05,0:03:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撿回一條命了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐井
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.99,0:03:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山椒魚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.14,0:03:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然用事前藏好的防禦傀儡包住炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓爆炸的威力大大減弱了 嗯 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把他當炸彈…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.84,0:04:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼意見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.27,0:04:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就你這樣的廢物也想接佐助的班
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒力量就少逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.26,0:04:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要靈魂還被束縛在這世上 就能無數次復活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會繼續用他做炸彈的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.45,0:04:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想傷害你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.91,0:04:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明已經死了 從根解放了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抹殺感情的鍛煉系統
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.81,0:04:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將兩個從小一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.17,0:04:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情同手足的人撫養長大後　
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終讓其互相殘殺　
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.87,0:04:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是木葉根的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中無心則無惑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是真正強大的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為根的你們和我很相似
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.11,0:05:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自以為是地畫畫 你當自己是藝術家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藝術就是爆炸 再來一發華麗的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你試試看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.25,0:05:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 我想讓你看一幅畫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.38,0:05:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪幅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.41,0:05:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,0:05:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有畫完呢 再等等嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑秘技…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.01,0:06:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話…只能自爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.55,0:06:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然總用究極藝術感覺有點不值錢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.50,0:06:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也沒辦法 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷遁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機機三發
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好 重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來我會一直用傀儡術束縛他們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們想辦法對付佐井的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很清楚…在根的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本和哥哥有一場生死之戰…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時…沒完成的決鬥…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的苦無 我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,0:07:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是在空中被撞飛了 真不走運
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運氣也是實力的一種
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天做飯的就是你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.04,0:07:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那就好…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來到這裡有多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.59,0:08:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會一直住在這裡嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.43,0:08:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像除了信哥哥和團藏大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒見過其他人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.77,0:08:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日子都過得記不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣也不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠和信哥哥這樣生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.45,0:08:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.97,0:08:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拆開看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.13,0:09:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…素描冊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很早之前就想要了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.16,0:09:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前逛街的時候買的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.08,0:09:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定了 我要在這上面畫我們的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要將我和信哥哥的故事做成畫集
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.34,0:09:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 完成了要給我看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人之間的約定 絕對要遵守哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您說什麼 團藏大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來你們兩人要全力以赴 一決生死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.30,0:09:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你們的最終考試
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.55,0:10:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是根的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.43,0:10:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若三日後你倆都活著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又或者兩人一同下山的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就做好一起去死的準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 無法和哥哥戰鬥…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.74,0:10:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話…我就殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.48,0:11:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.42,0:11:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要活下去的話 你太仁慈了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.55,0:11:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.14,0:11:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過要活下去的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已病入膏肓…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那趕緊治療啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.51,0:11:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的 我研究過自己的病
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種病無藥可治
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.41,0:11:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,團藏大人並不知道這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.37,0:11:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就告訴團藏大人 已經幹掉我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.55,0:11:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:12:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道根的最終測試是殺掉同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會瞞著病情撐到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想交手時故意失手被傷然後認輸…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在連這點體力都不剩了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…我也知道必須要和你一戰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.26,0:12:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我無法下手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扼殺你的心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則你早晚會被任務壓垮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 連我的份一起活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.15,0:13:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是能自行了斷的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.67,0:13:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准哭 都讓你扼殺自己的心了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想看看你畫完的畫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那場決鬥嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.78,0:13:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好嗎 佐井
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐井 這是你現在的名字啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.46,0:14:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經完成了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於看到曾經想看的畫了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.52,0:14:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的畫讓我被束縛的靈魂得到解脫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐井 好好珍惜直呼你名字的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.41,0:14:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.33,0:14:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,線沒反應了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠍 我已經聽小櫻說過你的作戰方式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時和千代婆婆一起的女人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此乃吾之禁術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來以為再也不會用到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但世事總是不盡人意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.07,0:15:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就以此來了結吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數量可觀啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.22,0:16:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傀儡師的實力在於操縱的傀儡數量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.87,0:16:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代婆婆的奧義十指之術
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是僅憑一人就能攻下一座城的傀儡集
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白秘技.十機近松之集
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.13,0:16:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傀儡術 初代操演者文左衛門的十大作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起的傀儡集
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.80,0:17:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以這個攻下了一個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.24,0:17:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤秘技.百機操演
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的強大源自於你的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.27,0:17:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您曾想抹去靈魂成為傀儡 卻未能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你製造的傀儡卻擁有不朽的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我能感覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今你雖有肉身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻墮落成真正的傀儡 普通的人偶而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.97,0:17:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該是操縱傀儡的一流忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.19,0:17:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是被人操縱的廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兜是你當時所用的間諜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而此刻你卻為他所控…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傀儡師一旦被操縱就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.75,0:17:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是你 還是操縱著你的兜…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.13,0:17:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意志絕不會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.13,0:18:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為真正的傀儡師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操縱著同一個蠍就更是如此了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.26,0:18:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的技術以及所創造的傀儡才是真正的不朽之物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那寄宿著靈魂的傀儡會借操演者之手代代相傳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是…我所渴求的藝術形態嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.01,0:18:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠍大哥 別被這些傢伙的花言巧語蒙蔽 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藝術是瞬間的光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.37,0:18:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藝術就是爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在聽嗎 蠍大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.07,0:18:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄宿著創造者的靈魂嗎…確實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:18:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勘九郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.93,0:18:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.58,0:19:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父和母的傀儡也托付給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待你離世時 再授予後人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.80,0:19:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.74,0:19:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠍大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.76,0:19:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是活祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說穢土轉生是不死之術…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.88,0:19:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是兜解除了術吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.17,0:19:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我出去 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.01,0:19:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不是那麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠍已經不在了 但煩人的傢伙還在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,號稱完美的穢土轉生…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:19:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來也存在漏洞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.36,0:20:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的感情是無法簡單束縛的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.53,0:20:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 現在才開始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐井 重 佐治 立刻準備奇襲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.05,0:20:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.68,0:20:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穢土轉生…是尚有諸多不明的術
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過如此一來也大致清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.89,0:20:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑 你去前線吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.32,0:20:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要隱藏起來集中施術
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.04,0:20:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然潛入到如此接近根據地的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.04,0:21:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭如指掌的兜是故意引她來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.89,0:21:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死的兜…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.84,0:21:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始就籌劃將我和聯軍一併扳倒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被利用的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.06,0:22:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穢土轉生真的需要活人的身體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.22,0:22:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將這個忍術的一切都告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.82,0:22:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不願意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.65,0:23:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你渴求的東西非但一輩子都得不到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.07,0:23:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還得倒貼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.16,0:23:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如你的小命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.72,0:23:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集火影忍者疾風傳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.67,0:23:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穢土轉生的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.01,0:23:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我就解釋給你聽吧
